  "remarks": "\nInvolved in activities carried out on behalf of the former regime of Muammar Qadhafi implementing or connected to the repressive policies of that regime, including in the 1980s, Sayyid was involved in the dissident assassination campaign and allegedly responsible for several deaths in Europe. He is also thought to have been involved in arms procurement.",
